  <keyword>sqrt</keyword>
  <short_description>Square root.</short_description>
  <syntax>
    <syntax_item>R = sqrt(M)</syntax_item>
  </syntax>
  <param_input>
    <param_input_item>
      <param_name>M</param_name>
      <param_description>a variable</param_description>
    </param_input_item>
  </param_input>
  <param_output>
    <param_output_item>
      <param_name>R</param_name>
      <param_description>result of sqrt: square root.</param_description>
    </param_output_item>
  </param_output>
  <description>
    <p><b>sqrt</b> calcule la racine carrée.</p>
    <p>Pour les nombres réels positifs :</p>
    <latex>\sqrt{x}</latex>
    <p>Pour les nombres complexes <b>z = x + iy</b> :</p>
    <latex>\sqrt{z} = \sqrt{r} e^{i\phi/2}</latex>
    <p>où</p>
    <latex>r = |z| = \sqrt{x^2 + y^2}</latex>
    <p>et</p>
    <latex>\phi = \arg(z) = \text{atan2}(y, x)</latex>
  </description>
